description:
Following on from the last episode, we learn about John the Baptist. John was the cousin of Jesus and played a crucial part in preparing the way for Jesus' ministry to flourish. He knew his role and was happy to decrease whilst Jesus' ministry increased. His life was cruelly taken from him, but his example of selfless service remains for us today.
